Package com.kpi.tuke.scql

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kpi.tuke.scql.View
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filterable, Performable
    public class View
extends java.lang.Object
implements Performable
    Class View holds the information about the view structure in databases. As defined in ISO7816-7, view contains a name, table to which it should refer, column names from the referred table and select filters.
